readable.content: a black dog jumping into some water to catch a red and blue Frisbee A black dog jumps into the water to get a Frisbee while a boat sits in the back . A dog is jumping into the water The black dog is wearing a red collar and is jumping into the water after a Frisbee . The black dog jumps above the water towards a Frisbee floating near a boat .
